# Walkthrough: RoboLedgers Ledger Core Initialization

This walkthrough demonstrates the first technical implementation of the **RoboLedgers Financial Constitution**. We have successfully built the "Ledger Core" and proven that it enforces the locked invariants.

## 1. Core Implementation
We established the foundational data structures and logic in the project workspace:
- **[transaction.ts](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/types/transaction.ts)**: Defined the [CanonicalTransaction](file:///g:/My%20Drive/RoboLedger%20-%20NEW/src/types/transaction.ts#24-46) object with CORE-IMMUTABLE and VERSIONED fields.
